rlm-switchbranch

Pick a local git branch with fzf and switch to it.

Pipes `git branch` into fzf and runs `git switch` on the
selected branch. The selection retains the leading marker
column from `git branch` output, but `git switch` tolerates the
extra whitespace for normal branches.

Must be run inside a git working tree. Aborting fzf cancels
without switching.

Aliases: switchbranch
